{
  "stem": "22836.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he tell me, they kill all of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How come, Louis-- Louis, you live?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Louis you live.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They killed everybody that was in your group?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They think they kill me, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They killed everybody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tie them up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister was asking them to take her to the cemetery, to Kolk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she always bring-- ask him to the cemetery, to the Kolk-- Kolki, you know, but they don't listen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they killed me, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They think they killed me, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he says, that means something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he ask me, where is Mayer?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he always know I go with Mayer together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, Mayer, there is little-- little, but he's all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't say Mayer-- I don't say Mayer is killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because Mayer--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to me, he was my protection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I get in to Ukrainians to get bread, or something, even I trust him, he have to know Mayer is alive, outside.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the other way, he can kill me, too, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can't trust nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always go with, him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mayer is alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they believe me, because they say they kill me, and I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is Mayer alive too?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then-- then after that, I see everything is done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went-- and my wife that time, the first wife, Anna, was by a girlfriend, a Polish girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was hiding there by--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was not with me, because she was very weak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometime, the girlfriend take her, and she washed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was there with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I went back to her, to my wife-- first wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
